query:
SELECT dr.id, dr.branchId, dr.date, dr.total, 
       (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM employeeRevenues er WHERE er.dailyRevenueId = dr.id) as employeeCount
FROM dailyRevenues dr 
WHERE dr.date >= '2026-01-01' AND dr.date <= '2026-01-07'
ORDER BY dr.date DESC;
